   Law:
   Store Is Kept
   As Defendant
   In Tobacco Suit
   ----
   By Suzanne Alexander and David Stipp
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
